#Point System for game

Characters: Teller(T), Inquirer(I)

Situation 1: Teller is told to lie. Teller wins / Inquirer loses
  Teller +5 Inquirer -5
Situation 2: Teller is told to be truthful. Teller wins / Inquirer loses
Situation 3: Teller is told to lie. T loses / I wins
Situation 4: Teller is told to be truthful. T loses / I wins
Situation 5: Teller is told to lie. Double Down. T wins / I loses
Situation 6: Teller is told to lie. Double Down. T loses / I loses 
